data.description: This is the Home for you. This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom and recently added a bonus room by enclosing the garage home is great for your family. This home is located only a few minutes away from downtown, shopping, medical and parks . This home is spacious and features the double fireplace,  granite counters in the kitchen, huge driveway. This home is perfect for family gatherings. The .33 Acre lot offers plenty of space for outdoor activities, The backyard is fenced,   Call for your showing today don't miss out on this Home its in the perfect location and is the perfect size for your family. Roof completed 2014 and AC 2013.
